Historical Events, Mysteries and Threats (roll a d20 or choose)
1. The death of an important figure. 11. The rise of a new military power.
2. Monsters are restless and aggressive. 12. Gods are forsaking the world.
3. A meteor will hit the planet. 13. A legendary monster appears.
4. The ocean levels are rising. 14. The world is plunged into darkness.
