2. Tower of sorcery. 12. Petrified forest.
3. Network of caverns or tunnels. 13. Forgotten labyrinth.
4. Ancient ship or airship. 14. Legendary island.
5. Inside a magitech colossus. 15. Bottomless pit.
6. Lost city. 16. Underwater shrine.
7. Great cathedral. 17. Inside an enormous creature.
8. Castle or fortress. 18. Another planet or dimension.
9. Steam-powered factory. 19. Sewers.
10. Luxurious mansion. 20. Prison.
Focal Element
1. A blessed weapon. 11. Vital information for the heroes.
2. An apocalyptic mechanism. 12. A forbidden ritual or spell.
3. A legendary monster. 13. The leader of a hostile faction.
4. A way to commune with an Arcanum. 14. An ancient and wise creature.
