DESIGNING RARE ARMORS AND SHIELDS
Creating a rare armor or shield is much simpler. Pick one of the items from the lists
on pages 132 to 133 and add a single Quality to it, which will increase its price by a
variable amount, as shown by the table below.
Once again, feel free to come up with new and unique special abilities for rare armors
and shields, using these as a reference.
