UNDEAD
DREAD URN Lv 5 w UNDEAD
A sepulchral urn, filled with old bones and inhabited by a restless
soul fueled by envy towards the living.
Typical Traits: cackling, fragile, floating, tiny.
DEX d10 INS d6 MIG d6 WLP d10 HP 50 w 25 MP 55 Init. 8
DEF +1 M.DEF +2 ' VU a b aIM E f VU i l VU b IM
BASIC ATTACKS
$ Urn Poke w【 DEX + MIG】 w【 HR + 5】 physical damage.
a Chaos Cackle w【 DEX + MIG】 w【 HR + 5】 dark damage and the target suffers shaken.
This attack targets Magic Defense.
SPECIAL RULES
Undead w The dread urn is immune to poisoned and HP recovery may harm them (page 305).
ZOMBIE Lv 5 w UNDEAD
The rotting remains of a humanoid, animated by dark magic and
driven by an insatiable hunger. Tough, but clumsy.
Typical Traits: creepy, mindless, rotting, slow.
DEX d6 INS d6 MIG d12 WLP d8 HP 70 w 35 MP 45 Init. 6
DEF +2 M.DEF +1 ' a b aIM E VU f VU i l VU b IM
BASIC ATTACKS
$ Ravenous Bite w【 DEX + MIG】 w【 HR + 5】 dark damage and the target suffers weak.
$ Zombie Rake w【 MIG + MIG】 w【 HR + 5】 physical damage.
SPECIAL RULES
Empty Mind w The zombie is immune to dazed, enraged, and shaken.
Undead w The zombie is immune to poisoned and HP recovery may harm it (page 305).
