SKELETAL MAGE Lv 10 w UNDEAD
Often acting as a necromancer’s lieutenants, these animated corpses
are gifted with nefarious intellect and can channel dark magic.
Typical Traits: ambitious, clever, knowledgeable, ruthless.
DEX d6 INS d8 MIG d8 WLP d10 HP 60 w 30 MP 70 Init. 5
DEF +2 M.DEF +4 ' a b aIM E VU f RS i RS l VU b IM
Equipment: staff, sage robe.
BASIC ATTACKS
$ Staff w【 WLP + WLP】 +1 w【 HR + 6】 physical damage and the mage recovers 5 MP.
SPELLS
h Umbra r w【 INS + WLP】 +1 w 10 × T MP w Up to three creatures w Instantaneous.
Each target suffers【 HR + 15】 dark damage.
Opportunity: Each target suffers shaken.
SPECIAL RULES
Undead w The skeletal mage is immune to poisoned and HP recovery may harm them (page 305).
SKELETAL SOLDIER Lv 10 w UNDEAD
Usually found guarding ancient ruins or serving a necromancer, these
creatures are ruthless and capable combatants.
Typical Traits: cruel, mindless, murderous, silent.
DEX d8 INS d8 MIG d10 WLP d6 HP 70 w 35 MP 40 Init. 6
DEF 12 M.DEF +0 ' a VU b aIM E VU f i l VU b IM
Equipment: bronze sword, bronze shield, brigandine.
BASIC ATTACKS
$ Bronze Sword w【 DEX + MIG】 +5 w【 HR + 11】 physical damage.
SPECIAL RULES
Empty Mind w The skeletal soldier is immune to dazed, enraged, and shaken.
Undead w The skeletal soldier is immune to poisoned and HP recovery may harm it (page 305).
