GHOUL Lv 15 w UNDEAD
Hulking corpses inhabited by a soul driven mad by a terrible curse.
Ghouls haunt graveyards and feed on the freshly deceased.
Typical Traits: aggressive, large, powerful, terrifying.
DEX d8 INS d6 MIG d12 WLP d6 HP 90 w 45 MP 45 Init. 7
DEF +0 M.DEF +0 ' a b aIM E f i l VU b IM
BASIC ATTACKS
$ Furious Claws w【 MIG + MIG】 +1 w【 HR + 10】 physical damage. This attack has multi (2).
$ Poison Breath w【 DEX + MIG】 +1 w【 HR + 5】 poison damage and the target suffers
poisoned.
SPECIAL RULES
Undead w The ghoul is immune to poisoned and HP recovery may harm them (page 305).
